description: Clearance of site and erection of 1 x part five, part seven, part eight and part eleven storey building and 1 x part thirteen, part fourteen and part fifteen storey building to provide 2293 sqm commercial floor space to create 49 affordable artist studios (B1) and 1384 sqm commercial floorspace falling under Use Classes A1, A2, A3, B1, B8, D1 / or D2 use plus 209 residential units (10xstudios, 55 x 1 bed, 64 x 2 bed, 53 x 3 bed, 20 x 4 beds and 7 x 5 beds including 71 affordable units),  62 x car parking spaces, (22 disabled), 6 x motorbike spaces, 290 x cycle spaces with access, refuse/recycling facilities and ancillary landscaping.
